月8日，山东省体育局印发了《省优秀运动队思想道德和作风建设专项教育工作实施方案》的通知，其中明确了对畸形“饭圈文化”侵袭严重等突出问题开展专项教育。 采写：南都记者 冯奕然山东省体育局回应“孙颖莎来者不善”争议表述：系被恶意解读_陈梦_文章_南都"},"attached_info":"CkAItJrg/vCt2qltEAMaCTExMDIxNTA1NyDKjMa2BjAAOKkCQBtyCTY2NTcxODc4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"4.8 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53cacf657496f468d24c5553a53059fc_b.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1725164425.428993","card_id":"Q_665834734","target":{"id":665834734,"title":"24-25赛季英超第 3 轮，哈弗茨破门，阿森纳 1:1 布莱顿，赖斯争议红牌，如何评价这场比赛?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665834734","type":"question","created":1725110907,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":54,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[7813,8040,1912335,1932980],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8ItJrg/vCt2qltEAMaCTExMDI0MTAwMiD7tMy2BjAAODZAHHIJNjY1ODM0NzM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"4.7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-436ac46a032e9e9c40d2c5d869582029_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1725164425.429327","card_id":"Q_346365934","target":{"id":346365934,"title":"一个人承受得了多少屈辱？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/346365934","type":"question","created":1568675234,"answer_count":49,"follower_count":119,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[994,21182],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在你还没能力的时候谁都会欺负你，践踏你。"},"attached_info":"Cj4ItJrg/vCt2qltEAMaCDM5MjQ3OTA1IKKrgOwFMAA4d0AdcgkzNDYzNjU5MzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]}],"description":{"time":"2024-09-01 12:2